{"tid":2498821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓大學生在日本大使館前剃光頭 抗議日本排放核廢水入海","createTime":"2021-04-21T12:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T12:32:52.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ca87c075dd5845513b1043be9a126e37ce83e808","tid":2498821,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"日本政府拍板決定，預計2年後開始把福島核電廠的廢水排放入海，引起南韓等鄰國抗議。本週二（20日），有30多名南韓大學生在日本駐首爾大使館前，以剃光頭來表達抗議。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透報導，儘管南韓目前有禁止10人以上聚會的禁令，南韓警察也舉著警告標語執法，仍擋不住南韓學生前往日本駐首爾大使館抗議。而剃光頭的抗議者身上亦披著布條譴責日本，並呼籲日本應該放棄排放核廢水的決定。<br />\n<br />\n南韓政府曾於上週譴責日本的決定，並召開相關會議，研議向國際法院請願；美國氣候特使凱瑞（John Kerry）曾於18日表示，他堅信日方與國際原子能機構（IAEA）會對此保持緊密合作，且合作會更加緊密。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3506197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3506197&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=36512125\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3506197&h=9b83a7aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3506197</a>"},{"pid":"55d3daef22739b0741baa10fd6015672048daa74","tid":2498821,"uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"加埋接力絕食，效果更佳"},{"pid":"726ef6f9117e01702c65abca7007c928b5d4087c","tid":2498821,"uid":397108,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"日本人不吃這套"},{"pid":"c19c586bde7e190a9ee26434684f13ca9fa53dba","tid":2498821,"uid":84415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"咁撚有威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a7d81929a47a037b854cc079baa450d7cc7055","tid":2498821,"uid":76747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"咁做有咩用"},{"pid":"2ea5ad9